# ORION — Main Summary

## Project Overview
ORION is a futuristic AI desktop assistant built with Electron that serves as a multi-agent operator for coding, business management, scheduling, and general conversation. It uses cloud AI APIs (Groq, Gemini, OpenRouter) with a 3-column "Mission Control" UI.

