## Architecture — The Chat Flow

```
User types message
        │
        ▼
renderer.js: sendMessage()
        │  window.orion.chat(message, sessionId)
        ▼
preload.js: chat(message)
        │  ipcRenderer.invoke('orion:chat', message, sessionId)
        ▼
main.js: orion:chat handler
        │  brain.asyncChat(finalMessage, history, onChunk)
        ▼
ai-brain.js: asyncChat()
        ├── agentRegistry.executeTask() → Agent handles it? → Return response
        └── router.route() → _groqStream() → Groq API → Stream response
        │
        ▼
Returns { response, mode, brain } to renderer
        │
        ▼
renderer.js: Displays response in chat
```

### Current AI Routing (settings.json)
```
localFirst: false → Ollama Offline → Groq (default brain)
                                       ├── Fallback: OpenRouter Claude
                                       ├── Fallback: OpenRouter Grok
                                       └── Fallback: Gemini
```

